premise_source_doc_sentence: Haim Saban  (  -LSB- səˈbɑːn -RSB- חיים סבן born October 15 , 1944  )  is an Israeli-American media proprietor , investor , philanthropist , musician , record , film & television producer .

premise_source_doc_sentence: Saban is the founder of Saban Entertainment , producer and distributor of children 's television programs in the US such as Power Rangers .

claim: Haim Saban is a television producer of Israeli decent from the United States.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Saban Entertainment  (  along with Saban International , which operated outside the US  )  was a worldwide-served independent American-Israeli television production company formed in 1983 by music and television producers Haim Saban and Shuki Levy as `` Saban Productions '' , a U.S. subsidiary of `` Saban International Paris ''  (  later SIP Animation  )  .
